title: Four vehicle crash causes delays on motorway
text:
6 comments 
PART of a Hampshire motorway is blocked following a four vehicle pile-up – including a lorry. 
The truck and three cars were in collision on the M3 northbound carriageway between junction 12 Eastleigh and 11 at Winchester at 7.58am. 
Police say no one has been injured. 
• More details on our live traffic and travel service >> Share article 
But officers have sealed off one lane while crews work to recover the vehicles which include a Range Rover a Vauxhall and a Nissan. 
It is causing delays for motorists at the height of the rush hour. Promoted Stories Four vehicle crash causes delays on M3 motorway Sorry, an error occurred.
